Package de.mdelab.simulator.impl

Implementation of the generic simulation framework.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InjectionController
    Controls the injection of issues into the model using the Scenario provided by the user.
    LogUtil
    Log utility class of the simulator.
    PerformanceEntry
    Simulation result entry of the performance of one run of the feedback loop in one simulation round.
    PerformanceResults
    The performance results of the simulation as the individual execution times in milliseconds of each feedback loop run in each simulation round.
    SimulationResults<T extends SimulationResultsEntry>
    Collection of SimulationResultsEntry objects collected over the whole simulation.
    SimulationResultsEntry
    An entry of results collected during the simulation.
    Timer
    Timer for measuring the elapsed wall-clock time.
    UtilityEntry
    Simulation result entry of the utility of the managed system at a specific point in time and simulation round.
    UtilityResults
    The utility results of the simulation as the individual utilities of the managed system in each simulation round and at a specific point in time.
